---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="About — Ian Liew" description="About Ian Liew — Director at Deloitte, solutions architect, AI transformation leader based in Hong Kong.">
  <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-6 pt-20 sm:pt-28 pb-12 sm:pb-16">
    <p class="text-xs font-semibold tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500 mb-8">About</p>

    <h1 class="text-3xl font-light text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-50 tracking-tight mb-10">Ian Liew</h1>

    <div class="space-y-5 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-12">
      <p>
        I started out as a builder. Computer Science degree, hands on keyboards, making things work. That foundation never left — it just grew to include bigger systems, more complex stakeholders, and higher stakes.
      </p>
      <p>
        Over 20 years I've worked across consulting, startups, and large enterprise — in Melbourne, Sydney, Houston, Hong Kong, and Shanghai. I've led data platform builds, enterprise migrations, automation deployments, and agentic AI programs. The common thread isn't the technology; it's the job of translating what an organisation needs to <em>become</em> into something that actually exists and runs.
      </p>
      <p>
        What I've learned is that transformation fails at the seams — between strategy and delivery, between the system and the people who use it. The technology is rarely the hard part. The hard part is designing the journey: what gets built when, how teams adopt it, what "done" actually means at each stage. I architect both sides.
      </p>
      <p>
        Today I'm a Director at Deloitte, working on AI-driven transformation programs. I lead architecture, delivery, and release — turning emerging technology into capabilities that organisations can actually operate and scale.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="border-t border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-800 pt-8">
      <p class="text-xs font-semibold tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500 mb-4">Links</p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
        {[
          { label: 'LinkedIn', href: 'https://linkedin.com/in/ianliew' },
          { label: 'GitHub', href: 'https://github.com/ianliew' },
          { label: 'Twitter', href: 'https://twitter.com/ianliew_' },
          { label: 'Email', href: 'mailto:i@ianliew.com' },
        ].map(({ label, href }) => (
          <a href={href} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"
             class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 hover:text-gray-900 dark:hover:text-gray-50 underline underline-offset-2 transition-colors">
            {label}
          </a>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Base>
